BBNaija reality star, Mercy Eke and Ike have talked about their love life and plans for their future after leaving the house. During the interview, Mercy while shading Tacha who was disqualified from the show after a fight, told aspiring Big Brother Naija housemates not to get disqualified and also work on their anger issues. However, her advice has caused outrage on social media with some people insinuating that she is mocking Tacha who was disqualified in the BBNaija house. Mercy said: “It is better to be evicted than to be disqualified” See the full video below: Source